Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:31.37,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(167,995)}{\fad(650,650)}{\blur4.5\be2}邂逅…为命运增色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镜子啊镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个王国里最美丽的姑娘 是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉冀王子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？ 萨柯契
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此人不叫镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是城里的情报贩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如实回答所见所闻 叫他镜子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过胡闹也请适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也别再磨蹭赶紧说出情报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个丹巴伦王国中最美丽的女子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那位姑娘如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个姑娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生来有着异常罕见而美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红苹果一般的鲜红秀发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为白雪的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘记吃药哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤系先生 多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 接下来是奇诺婆婆的药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来观赏白雪那美丽的秀发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来养养眼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你难得过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你调合下补开的药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好采到些不错的药草 顺便带上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在也成为一位出色的药剂师了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想让你去世的祖父祖母也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 奇诺婆婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来了 锅还坐在炉子上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等再送去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落下东西了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉冀王子的爱妾？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 也就是王子的小妾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样的市井女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为发色就被迎娶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让王子蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那位拉冀王子看中的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之明天就会正式迎接你入宫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在今晚之内做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇诺婆婆的腰背止痛药和呼吸道消炎药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里家说是父亲和小宝宝有些感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 丹巴伦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下 请问有谁在家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不能随便闯进别人家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天也暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子也饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光秀 木木 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你又从这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 千
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤了没？没撞到头吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1加1是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你是谁来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是光秀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 好像是这个名字来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木木 你也跟着瞎胡闹什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这森林深处做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 那个我只是个离家出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿着没有人烟的路走罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的头发很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 经常被这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的右手受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一名药剂师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身边带着敷药 你不嫌弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种说不定是毒药的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然拿出来谁会去用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是森林里的小矮人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能那么轻易相信别人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这里没你什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了就赶快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起话来居高临下的人真是到哪里都有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可惜 我没有带毒药出门的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千 这次是你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉了 我叫千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请多关照 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说了我着地失败有一半是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是间空屋 是我们平常玩耍的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后那边下国际象棋输掉的是光秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松获胜的是木木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千 为什么看都没看就一口咬定是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上的确输了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很熟练啊 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了我是药剂师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你这位药剂师为什么要离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什么了不起的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微去散个步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么跟着来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让受伤的姑娘一个人进森林有违绅士之名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了学习草药已经习惯了山林所以没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里时间和空气的流动与城里不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里感觉很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这个我能懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你很坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有束头发特别长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是没剪干净
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 千 能帮我剪一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便剪剪就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪女孩子头发这种事我可办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃一头长发和你离家出走有什么关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我其中缘由的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被要求去当爱妾？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小在花柳之地长大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以挥霍出名的有钱人家的少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得红发很罕见就想把我留在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他来说就像在水果摊买苹果一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请他看残发看个够
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把头发留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这决定下的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸亏你切断了和那下三滥的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是你最重要的红色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的红色？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的红色也就是命运的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这次惹了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但下次说不定能引来意料不到的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法很不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃然起敬了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然看来不是什么可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此 千还很中意她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我用来扎发束的丝带
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你是从丹巴伦王国来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送来这个的人为了迎接你已经来到国境附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是个很执着的绅士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你笑得出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事有严重到要越境逃跑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方也有点来头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是丹巴伦的第一王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉冀！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫做这个的笨蛋王子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋名气竟然响彻邻国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方这个来头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必找人调查了过境记录之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然做到这个份上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个只要想要得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定要得到的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至能轻易将人关进笼中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始变质了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这红色也已无法保持了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我随便说说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没教养啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能这样吧 千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃的话自己去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要边吃边说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没叫你们吧 闪一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太伤人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我说了傻话 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪 这苹果你千万别吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:14:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木木光秀 别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有解毒药吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 只有这些的话不够用来调配
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 吃下苹果的不是白雪小姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某位大人手上拥有解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能请你跟我走一趟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 的确惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来留下的红发是真货呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我朋友的解药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢 白雪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来骇人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向白雪你求爱 却把你吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事似乎成了市井和王宫里的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不定会因此名声扫地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是将你作为罪人处理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是承认了谣言是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以为了挽回我的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请你主动请求成为我的爱妾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说只是一介市井女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是我不忍女性蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所接受的解决方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻听？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 首先是解药
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能赐予我朋友解药吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉冀王子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要白雪小姐首肯 我就立马派人送去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我派人将这个送去慰问？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的红色也就是命运的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这次惹了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但下次说不定能引来意料不到的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了对我说这番话的人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与如此令我赏心悦目的姑娘分开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并让她远走他方实在可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 这真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉冀王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你随意处置我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 还不退下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反对！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别再说出那些戏言 来玷污这位女孩的耳朵了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我把这个绑上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个你的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以防万一 我身体对毒药已经有了一定的抗性了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吃下毒药的男人就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不幸的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来计划让白雪小姐不能动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是送来苹果的罪魁祸首吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意你说话的语气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你身份悬殊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹巴伦王国第一王子 拉冀·谢纳扎德殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 虽然麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我重新自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我是克拉利涅斯王国第二王子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千·威斯塔利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王…王子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我是谁吗？1加1是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪 我很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过竟然会被临国的王子下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我真是想都没有想到啊 拉冀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 哪里有我下毒的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要多少有多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在官方场合来一辩真伪也无妨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就来做个交易吧 笨蛋王子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不想让这次的愚蠢行径公之于众
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就发誓不再和白雪有任何牵扯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且不许再叫白雪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是白雪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了我发誓 现在就发下誓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪 你也有很多话想说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想抱怨的话只有现在了 大胆说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉冀王子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给你的慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看你都已经吓得脚软了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是 赶快给千解药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对千而言 我只不过是你的毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我应该笑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我吃的毒苹果和你都是红色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 白雪你不需要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是千自己吃下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们和千的考虑不周
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光秀他还哭着说如果千死了自己也跟着去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别揭穿我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吃水果就让光秀先帮我削皮再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚是这个话题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪 还记得我在森林里说的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我个人而言 我现在更乐意认为能和你在一起是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你自己走进的森林里遇见了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我们相交并且想要守护对方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是仅限此刻的毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是今后的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是能由我自己来决定的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如我的命运也是由我自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出决定之后能否走上这条道路也是看自己对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千 你这人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想法果然很不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是想法 是生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的回答呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是属于自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只愿这次邂逅之路的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻开故事的书页声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同重叠的脚步声一般久久回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:23:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白雪 我们总算见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.89,0:24:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉利涅斯真是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.17,0:24:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？白雪不在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定来这个国家的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.59,0:24:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不继续逃跑了吗？红发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:10.97,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,713)}第2话 走向心动之处